    Posted on Sunday, March 04 @ 01:35:58 EST by <a href="http://www.noows.com">zamtil</a><font size=2>Contributed by: <a href="user.php?op=userinfo&uname=zamtil">zamtil</a></font></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><br><a href="search.php?query=&topic=33"><img src=images/topics/announcements.gif border=0 Alt="Announcements" align=right hspace=10 vspace=10></a>Many of you submitted questions regarding Furor's possible retirement from EverQuest.  It's close, but he's giving Verant a final-chance to rectify some of their more recent mistakes, namely healing aggros.  Basically, Tuesday's patch will be make-or-break day, not only for Furor, but perhaps a large number of EverQuest FoH members.  
<br><br>
