I was pointing out that, by following events in Norrath, its easy to see throughout a 2 year period that once the big guilds like FoH get into the routine of taking down the boss/uber/whatever mob easily, it doesn't take too long before these mobs are buffed up or something is nerfed. All in the name of balance offcourse. <br>
And that is what Furor meant to say as well, patches/nerfs etc have been done to make things more difficult for the big boys, therefore they have indirectly had something to do with those patches.<br>
<br>
Hope this clears up the point I was trying to make (as a neutral bystander I might add, since none of this affects me... yet).<br>
<br>
Ryuen <br>
